  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently the generated resources are not very gitops friendly.\r\n\r\n- [ ] The resources are not idempotent (affected by commit, date and user).\r\n- [ ] The resources are generated under `target` which is usually not version controlled.\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nWe should disable the presence of non-idempotent labels by default.\r\nWe should also generate resources somewhere in the module root. Maybe `.kubernetes` or something like this.",
